name: Nautical Sailor Style Dress
description:
Very sweet little sailor style 1950's dress. 
Short sleeve,  knee length dress with red & blue pattern on a white background. 
Peter-Pan style collar with tie.  
A-line skirt with slightly fitted waist. 
Side zip fastening.
100 % Cotton. 
Approximately a UK size 10-12
30" waist
36" bust
44" length (just below the knee)

name: Green Blossom Tea Dress
description:
Adorable 1940s style floral tea dress. 
Beautiful jade green colour with pretty blossom pattern. 
Button through, short sleeve, hangs just below the knee.  
Super flattering, lovely fitted shirt waisted shape (but with slight elastic in the waist for comfort).
Polyester - cotton mix but looks and feels like crepe. 
In the style of the 1940s but is from 1980s. 

UK size 12-14 approximately. 
31" waist
40" bust 
44" length

PERFECT CONDITION. NO FLAWS. 
(belt not included)

name: Navy Floral Tea Dress
description:
Navy tea dress with pink flowers. 
Late 1940s calf length dress with elbow length sleeves & pintuck shoulders.  Zip fastening. 
Really pretty floral pattern in viscose fabric. 
Panel waist with four fabric covered buttons. 
VERY flattering. 

UK Size 14 approximately. 
waist 39"
bust 36"
length 45"
PERFECT CONDITION. NO FLAWS.

name: 1960s Floral Shift Dress
description:
Super cute 1960s floral shift dress. 
Grey and black flowers on an olive green background. 
100% Cotton. 
Fitted dress with slight drop waist & peter-pan collar. 
Handmade in the 1960s. 
Full length sleeves. 

UK Size 12 approximately. 
waist (drop waist) 38"
bust 42"
length 37.5"

FANTASTIC CONDITION. 
(Belt not included)

name: Pretty Lemon Dress
description:
Very sweet lemon coloured tea dress with pretty little floral pattern. 
1940's style (from 1980s probably)
Calf length dress. Zip and cute button fastening. 
Three-quarter length sleeve with button on cuff.
Very flattering panelled bust and nipped in waist. 
Loose around the top but with fitter shoulders and nipped in waist.
Viscose fabric. 

UK size 10-12 approximately. 
28" waist
42" bust
47" length 

FLAWLESS CONDITION.
